    <osa:InvokeCode PipelineOutput="{x:Null}" Code="   System.Data.SqlClient.SqlConnection CN = new System.Data.SqlClient.SqlConnection();
   //string connString = "Data Source=10.10.30.13;Initial Catalog=RPA_DB;Persist Security Info=True;User ID=RPA;Password=Rpa!@#$Te@m";
            string SQL_Str = "Data Source=10.10.30.115;Initial Catalog=MIS_DB;Persist Security Info=True;User ID=RPA;Password=eU($zfA}mj~m6H";
            string cmd =@"SELECT        [PRACTICE CODE], [PRACTICE NAME], [PROVIDER FIRST NAME], [PROVIDER MIDDLE NAME], [PROVIDER LAST NAME], NPI, [LICENSE NUMBER], [PRACTICE STATE], 

CASE WHEN ISNULL(F.[LICENSE NUMBER],'') = '' THEN 'Missing Input' else '' end [EXECUTION STATUS], 
CASE WHEN ISNULL(F.[LICENSE NUMBER],'') = '' THEN 'License number not available' else '' end [EXPLAINATION (IF ANY)]
FROM            (SELECT DISTINCT 
                                                    P.Practice_Code AS [PRACTICE CODE], P.Prac_Name AS [PRACTICE NAME], PR.Provid_FName AS [PROVIDER FIRST NAME], ISNULL(PR.Provid_Middle_Name, '') AS [PROVIDER MIDDLE NAME], 
                                                    PR.Provid_LName AS [PROVIDER LAST NAME], ISNULL(PR.NPI, '') AS NPI, ISNULL
                                                        ((SELECT        TOP (1) LICENSE_NUMBER
                                                            FROM            Credentialing_Documents
                                                            WHERE        (PROVIDER_CODE = PR.Provider_Code) AND (DOCUMENT_TYPE_ID IN ('ML013', 'BC018')) AND (ISNULL(LICENSE_NUMBER, '') <> '') AND (ISNULL(DELETED, 0) = 0)), '') AS [LICENSE NUMBER], 
                                                    P.Prac_State AS [PRACTICE STATE], '' AS [EXECUTION STATUS], '' AS [EXPLAINATION (IF ANY)]
                          FROM            Practices AS P INNER JOIN
                                                    Providers AS PR ON PR.Practice_Code = P.Practice_Code AND ISNULL(PR.Deleted, 0) = 0 AND ISNULL(PR.Is_Active, 1) = 1 LEFT OUTER JOIN
                                                    Credentialing_Documents AS CD ON CD.PROVIDER_CODE = PR.Provider_Code AND ISNULL(CD.DELETED, 0) = 0 AND CD.DOCUMENT_TYPE_ID IN ('ML013', 'BC018')
                          WHERE        (ISNULL(P.Deleted, 0) = 0) AND (P.Is_Active = 1) AND (P.Is_Active = 1) AND (P.Prac_State = 'KY')) AS F  ORDER BY [EXECUTION STATUS] DESC";
            if (CN.State == System.Data.ConnectionState.Open)
                CN.Close();
            CN.ConnectionString = SQL_Str;

            System.Data.DataSet MyDataSet = new System.Data.DataSet();
            try
            {
                System.Data.SqlClient.SqlDataAdapter MyDataAdapter = new System.Data.SqlClient.SqlDataAdapter(cmd, SQL_Str);
                MyDataAdapter.Fill(MyDataSet);
                TblInventory =  new System.Data.DataTable();
                TblInventory = MyDataSet.Tables[0];
            }
            catch (Exception ex)
            {
                string s = ex.Message;
